.\" Carsten Kunze, 2016
.Dd August 5, 2016
.Dt XPNAME 1
.Sh NAME
.Nm xpname
.Nd open pname with mouse support in a separate xterm
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Ar "pname options"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
There are use cases for
.Nm pname
where it is desirable to start it in a separate X window.
.Nm
just starts
.Do Nm xterm Fl e Dc
with
.Nm pname
and the
.Ar "pname options"
as argument and enables mouse support.
File names with spaces need to be enclosed in single or double quotes
.Po Sq Li \(aq
or
.Sq Li \(dq
.Pc
.Em and
the spaces needs to be protected with a backslash
.Pq Sq \(rs .
